---
title: Crispy Chickpea and Tomato Stew with Grilled Pesto-Cheese Tortillas
description: Roasting chickpeas in the oven gives them a crispy texture and nutty flavor. They’re perfect sprinkled over this herby tomato soup. The best part? The cheesy tortillas for dipping, of course!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/crispy-chickpea-and-tomato-stew-0e13452e.jpg
